#!/usr/bin/env python
# Time-stamp: <2011-09-08 11:50:38 Tao Liu>

"""Description: Fine-tuning script to call broad peaks from a single bedGraph track for scores.

Copyright (c) 2011 Tao Liu <taoliu@jimmy.harvard.edu>

